---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import SiteFooter from '../components/SiteFooter.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Us - Share Text Pad"
  description="Learn about Share Text Pad and our mission to make collaborative note sharing simple, fast, and accessible."
>
  <div class="min-h-screen overflow-x-hidden">
    <Navbar />
    <main id="main-content" class="mx-auto w-full max-w-4xl px-4 py-10 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <section class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/85 p-6 text-zinc-700 shadow-[0_24px_80px_-52px_rgba(0,0,0,0.55)] dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900/85 dark:text-zinc-300 sm:p-8">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100">About Us</h1>
        <div class="mt-5 space-y-4 text-sm leading-7 sm:text-base">
          <p>
            Share Text Pad was created to solve a simple problem: people need a fast way to write together and share notes online
            without friction. Most tools are either too heavy for quick collaboration or too limited for practical team use.
          </p>
          <p>
            We built Share Text Pad as a focused online notepad for real-time collaboration. You can create a note instantly,
            share it using a link or QR flow, and edit with others live. There is no complicated onboarding, and the interface
            stays clean so teams can focus on content instead of setup.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our goal is to keep collaboration simple, dependable, and accessible across desktop and mobile browsers. We continue
            improving performance, editing experience, and reliability so Share Text Pad remains useful for students, teams,
            creators, and anyone who needs to move ideas quickly.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <SiteFooter />
  </div>
</Layout>
